dBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T05:40:31.000Z","msg":"34歲退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"379dc6256f41da390bd31d75432ceb4d35a344bf","tid":175158,"uid":11428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T06:20:46.000Z","msg":"滙豐「肥雞餐」是3個月人工加上按年資每年經驗獲得三分之二個月之薪酬作賠償。<br />\n<br />\n計遣散費有冇15000ceiling 先，如果有，只係法例要求，肥乜撚野"}]}